  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0bae\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "International cooperation can only be achieved through a stable government - Imtiaz Pakheer Markar",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The solution to the political and economic crisis in the country is to create a stable, inclusive government.",
        "Imtiaz Baqir Markar, a Member of Parliament for the main opposition party, said that only through this could the cooperation of the international community and the International Monetary Fund be secured.",
        "He was speaking at a press conference at the United People's Power office on Sunday (26).",
        "Sri Lanka is facing an economic crisis that no other country on the Asian continent is facing. The country's economy has plummeted.",
        "The country today is in a state of massive crisis due to irresponsible decisions regarding agriculture and tax policy.",
        "People have faced various hardships because of it. People do not know when this situation will erupt.",
        "False economic policies and resolutions, massive corruption scandals and human rights abuses have brought the international community to its knees today.",
        "Countries like Japan that maintain long-term friendships today stay away. Middle Eastern countries are also reluctant to help.",
        "In this situation, the people and the international community have lost faith in the current government. The international community can no longer be deceived.",
        "At present there is a need to end the economic and political crisis and build economic stability.",
        "The cooperation of the international community can be obtained through the formation of an all-party government. Cooperation can be easily obtained if the international community acts in a trust-building manner.",
        "The International Monetary Fund expects a stable government that the people of the country want, not a government of corruption, bribery and looting. The state of instability will not receive international aid.",
        "He said we need to make it clear to the people and to the international community about the goal we need to move towards in the future."
      ],
